- features to be implemented:
raw data collection of temperature, humidity, luxometer, CO2 concentration via RTOS system
some raw data to be collected via linux kernel on beaglbone
go bot to obtain the data above

- details:
go server and database: AWS instance
custom bootloader for Linux and Bare Metal Embedded
ISC communication via USB: bare metal and linux embedded
kernel driver for some type of sensor
CI/CD
conteinerization

